tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  interaction_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    page_id UUID NOT NULL,
    start_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE page_interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_id INT REFERENCES pages(page_id),
  user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id),
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE analytics (
  analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_id INT REFERENCES pages(page_id),
  user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id),
  interaction_id INT REFERENCES user_interactions(interaction_id),
  analytics_data JSONB,
  analytics_date TIMESTAMP
);
